<TEXT>
bundledup preschoolers will sing carols in covent 
garden on saturday to remind shoppers that british journalist john 
mccarthy will spend another christmas as a hostage in lebanon 
the friends of john mccarthy hope the group of 4 year olds 
chosen because they have lived as long as he has been captive will 
catch news media attention and give a boost to the campaign for the 
television journalists release 
christmas is quite depressing because i think april is right 
round the corner said jill morrell mccarthys girlfriend at the 
time he was kidnapped on april 17 1986 
ms morrell also a television journalist has become the 
