collett hanged but his death has never been confirmed 
there are nine other western hostages in lebanon including 
terry anderson chief middle east correspondent for the associated 
press anderson was kidnapped march 16 1985 and has been in 
captivity the longest 
a small woman with a soft voice sparkling blue eyes and an easy 
smile ms morrell also displays a steely resolve that gained her 
