of britons 
but the last four months of the campaign which has now lasted 
longer than she and mccarthy were together have been particularly 
tough 
britains renewed diplmatic relations with iran and syria have 
brought few results 
false rumors of mccarthys imminent freedom have been especially 
frustrating after the euphoria surrounding the release of 
