cup of tea 
after three years together ms morrell and mccarthy had been 
about to buy an apartment and were thinking about marriage 
now she said she thought that when mccarthy was freed he might 
want to meet other women 
like keenan he might want to experience everything with new 
enthusiasm and make up for lost time 
