administration official quoted by the times 
iraq had warned commercial airliners to keep out of its airspace 
before the test but gave no reason 
the warning prompted israel and us officials to prepare their 
air forces to respond to an attack the newspaper said 
a lot of people were in their cockpits ready to go the 
