for lithuanian independence she said 
there was a worldwide outpouring of praise for shevardnadze a 
welcome guest in many capitals 
un secretarygeneral javier perez de cuellar told reporters 
on a personal basis i regret this he is a personal friend and 
he was very supportive of the united nations 
vatican radio hailed shevardnadze as the great architect of 
the soviet diplomacy that contributed to ending the cold war 
