support from people across the country the mail and calls that 
weve received have been 40 or 50to1 in strong support of the 
family he said 
at the same time antieuthanasia activists have converged on 
the redbrick rehabilitation center in this southwestern missouri 
community of 3400 and claimed the cruzan case as an extension of 
their cause 
