president mikhail s gorbachev met with eduard 
shevardnadze friday reportedly to discuss some way of keeping his 
longtime ally in the government following his sudden resignation as 
foreign minister 
in parliament reformers turned shevardnadzes unexpected 
resignation into a rallying cry a parade of speakers echoed the 
