theater home of the renowned ballet 
when the weather turns raw they walk around the block to the 
sadko cafe for hungarian wine salted fish and mushrooms cooked in 
sour cream 
sadko has more charm than utilitarian soviet cafes and one 
other advantage privacy its widely spaced tables allow discreet 
conversation and lamps reflect dim light onto a vaulted ceiling 
the golubye literally light blue ones russian slang 
for homosexuals are careful to leave in threes and fours 
its not a good idea to walk out of here alone because you 
can never tell whos waiting around the corner with a stick and a 
taste for blood said serezha 24 
