national which is counting heavily on circulation revenue 
only two weeks ago the newspaper told advertisers that it was 
reducing its circulation guarantee by 27 percent to 200000 copies 
the admission that it was not making its guaranteed average of 
275000 followed a review that resulted in the elimination of its 
sunday edition the dismissal of the circulation manager and two 
other top executives and layoffs of 18 other employees 
the paper is now publishing five times a week monday through 
friday 
