market totaled 27177 million shares 
trading was heavy both early in the morning and late in the 
session as professional investors engaged in maneuvers involving a 
group of expiring options and futures on stock indexes 
some of those contracts were settled on the basis of opening 
stock prices friday and others as of the close 
the witching hour which falls on the third friday of march 
june september and december was often a turbulent occasion for 
the market in years past but recently it has been taking place in 
more orderly style 
beyond that specialized activity analysts said it was an 
uneventful session with many investors getting an early start on 
the christmas holidays 
the markets will be open monday for an abbreviated christmas eve 
session ending at 2 pm est instead of the usual 4 pm close 
gainers among the blue chips included general electric up at 
58 exxon up rsqb at 50 american telephone amp telegraph up at 31 
international business machines up lsqb at 113 and ford motor up 
at 26rsqb 
